Windfish
  1. Use It Now
  2. Features
  3. Feedback

Overworld

Keep tabs on places you've been, places you're going and what was found when you got there!

  1. 50+ Map Markers
    1. Dungeons, chests, NPCs, entrances and landmarks
    2. Entrances are linked together; hovering shows both points
    3. Dungeon markers indentify their accessibility based on your current items
  2. Multiple overlays including entrances and collectibles
  3. Use different map images to ease your navigation

Items

Just activate an item or event and forget about pulling up your menu to check again!

  1. Different layout modes to expand on what you want to track
    1. Required Items & Dungeons
    2. Collectibles & Keys
    3. Pieces of Heart, Songs & Events
  2. Track the amount of potential unique chests in dungeons

Timer

Track your current run with just a click!

  1. Timer can start and stop whenever you like
  2. Save your best time to compare against later
  3. "Light Splitting" will show when you exceed your last best record

Broadcast

Options for Streamers and Re-Streamers

  1. Integrate with Twitch.tv chat
    1. Chat can activate anything in the Items tracker
    2. A bot at your control - joins and parts your channel at will
    3. Whitelisting features to prevent spam
    4. Virtually ZERO permissions required and no personal data needed
  2. Create a session with your friends
    1. Sessioning allows multi people to control the same tracker in real-time
    2. Broadcast your window and let someone across the world update it

Misc

Let the Windfish work for you!

  1. Visual customizations
  2. Persistent settings
